<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN290-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇai - karantai; tuṟai - kuṭinilaiyuraittal. oḷavaiyār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>  
    <div xml:id="PN290">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>ivaṟkīt tuṇmati kaḷḷē ciṉappō</l>
<l>riṉakkaḷiṟ ṟiyāṉai yiyaṟērk kuruci</l>
<l>ṉuntai tantaik kivaṉṟantai tantai</l>
<l>yeṭutteṟi ñāṭpi ṉimaiyāṉ ṟacca</l>
<l>ṉaṭutteṟi kuṟaṭṭi ṉiṉṟumāyn taṉaṉē</l>
<l>maṟappukaḻ niṟainta maintiṉō ṉivaṉu</l>
<l>muṟaippuḻi yōlai pōla</l>
<l>maṟaikkuvaṉ perumaniṟ kuṟittuvaru vēlē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Give toddy to this one [and] drink [yourself], oh lord</l>
<l>with an advancing chariot [and] male elephants from the angrily waring group! </l>
<l>For the sake of your father’s father his father’s father,</l>
<l>not one who blinks [an eye] in a fight that is raised [and] fought,</l>
<l>died standing like the axle box set up [and] cast by the carpenter.</l>
<l>Being a strong man amply praised for bravery, he too,</l>
<l>like the palm-leaf umbrella [protects] when it rains,</l>
<l>he will shield [you], great man, from the spears that come, aimed at you.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
